prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor painting of a humorous and lighthearted birthday scene. In the center, a cartoon illustration of an older Asian woman with short, dark, wavy hair and glasses (Lao Lao) is joyfully holding up a large, freshly baked birthday cake that is comically, slightly tilted as if she's about to drop it. She is wearing a green collared shirt. Standing next to her, looking on with a playful, slightly panicked expression, is a cartoon illustration of a young man with short dark hair, glasses, and a light beard (Jordan), reaching out as if to help steady the cake. He is wearing a grey t-shirt. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brushstrokes, and organic paint bleeds, capturing a candid and funny moment between them. In the center, in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Hope your day is as sweet as you (and this cake)!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
